content.content: Minister for Trade and Industry Gan Kim Yong to visit Abu Dhabi for the 13th World Trade Organization Ministerial Conference and related meetings
Minister for Trade and Industry Gan Kim Yong will be visiting Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates, from 25 to 27 February 2024.
